metadata.name: Asteri
metadata.description:
「 Starry Traveler 」 

Amidst the night sky,
I can sense the wonder of the whole world.
Beyond all those beautifully created,  
I stare at with curiosity,
Untraceable glittering specks,
Isolated flowers growing towards the sky.
The cosmic blanket, 
A velvet soon to explode into a thousand azurite stars.
That is my eternal canvas,
Searching for one like you.

 Leilani
